{
  "stem": "4187.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the child, when she was born, was-- was very, very badly incapacitated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It had no back passage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Interestingly, there was another case like that in Auschwitz where no back passage, so there must have been something, somehow-- well, I mustn't say that, because I don't know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But it's interesting that two-- two babies born with the same affliction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Anyway, this baby was born, no back passage, so it was quite obvious that that child had to die within 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she-- she was-- the mother was begging everyone not to tell the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But, of course, that was-- that was crazy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not that-- I don't think anyone told the Germans, but the child was crying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the Germans, of course, knew, and came to get the child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this woman fell on her knees and begged the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a scene out of a movie-- on her knees, holding on to the feet of the-- not to take the baby, but of course they did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she went blind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "From that day on, she was blind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But she was-- again, by a miracle, she survived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She was-- everyone, of course, was helping her, so the Germans didn't realize that she's blind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So she survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were in Duderstadt till April.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So that was quite a long stay there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- and I got very ill, very sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they put me into hospital there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then when I got better, they put me into the kitchen to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When I say 'they,' that's the Jewish head-- the Jewish head of the camp, who happened to be from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she-- she-- she said, you're going to-- you're going to go into the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So from then on, I was well fed.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
